title: Taylor Schilling, Carrie Brownstein reportedly dating | OITNB | The
text:
A source told Star magazine the pair have been texting, calling and visiting each other for four months.
Carrie stars in Portlandia. Source: Getty Images
Taylor plays Piper in OITNB. Source: Getty Images
They add Schilling even followed Brownstein’s band, Sleater-Kinney, to Scotland.
“She loves everything about Carrie,” the source told the magazine.
“It’s rare to find someone special in this business. They’re doing everything they can to keep the spark alive! This could be the real deal.”
The two actors have been posting cute snaps of each other to their Instagram accounts for several months.
Brownstein was formerly in a relationship with musician St. Vincent — who’s now dating Cara Delevingne.
Carrie stars in Portlandia and plays in band Sleater-Kinney. Source: Getty Images
Originally published as Piper from OITNB reportedly dating Portlandia star
